# AkshayTorch

Custom PyTorch extensions for memory-efficient deep learning on consumer GPUs.

Built to train diffusion models from scratch on RTX 3050 (6GB VRAM).

## Features (WIP)

- Memory-efficient attention mechanisms (Triton)
- Custom normalization layers (Welford's online algorithm)
- Gradient checkpointing utilities
- Mixed precision training helpers

## Why?

Training large models on limited VRAM requires custom optimizations
that standard libraries don't provide. This is my solution.

## Status

🚧 Work in progress - building while learning Triton and implementing DDPM
